@startuml Bug_Report_Submission

' ============================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM: Bug Report Submission
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' Team: Niway Tadesse, Abraham Asimamaw, Melkamu Tesfa
' Advisor: Yosef Worku
' ============================================

title Bug Report Submission - Sequence Diagram

actor Researcher
participant "Researcher Portal\n(Next.js)" as UI
participant "Bug Bounty Engine\n(FastAPI)" as BugBounty
participant "Redis Cache" as Redis
participant "MinIO Storage" as MinIO
participant "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Organization" as Org

== Authentication ==
Researcher -> UI: Login with credentials
UI -> BugBounty: POST /auth/login
BugBounty -> DB: Verify credentials
DB --> BugBounty: User data
BugBounty -> Redis: Store JWT session
BugBounty --> UI: JWT token
UI --> Researcher: Dashboard

== Browse Programs ==
Researcher -> UI: View available programs
UI -> BugBounty: GET /programs?status=active
BugBounty -> Redis: Check cache
alt Cache Hit
    Redis --> BugBounty: Cached programs
else Cache Miss
    BugBounty -> DB: Query active programs
    DB --> BugBounty: Program list
    BugBounty -> Redis: Cache programs
end
BugBounty --> UI: Program list
UI --> Researcher: Display programs

== Submit Bug Report ==
Researcher -> UI: Select program & fill report form
Researcher -> UI: Attach evidence (screenshots, videos)
UI -> MinIO: Upload files
MinIO --> UI: File URLs
UI -> BugBounty: POST /reports/submit\n{title, description, severity, files}

BugBounty -> DB: Check researcher eligibility
alt Not Eligible
    DB --> BugBounty: Eligibility failed
    BugBounty --> UI: Error: Not eligible
    UI --> Researcher: Show error message
else Eligible
    DB --> BugBounty: Eligible
    
    BugBounty -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    BugBounty -> DB: INSERT INTO reports
    BugBounty -> DB: INSERT INTO evidence
    BugBounty -> DB: UPDATE researcher stats
    BugBounty -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
    
    DB --> BugBounty: Report created (ID: #12345)
    
    BugBounty -> Redis: Invalidate program cache
    BugBounty -> Redis: Update researcher stats
    
    BugBounty -> Notification: Send notification
    Notification -> Org: Email: New report submitted
    Notification -> Researcher: Email: Report received
    
    BugBounty --> UI: Success (Report ID: #12345)
    UI --> Researcher: "Report submitted successfully!"
end

== View Report Status ==
Researcher -> UI: Check report status
UI -> BugBounty: GET /reports/12345
BugBounty -> Redis: Check cache
alt Cache Hit
    Redis --> BugBounty: Cached report
else Cache Miss
    BugBounty -> DB: Query report details
    DB --> BugBounty: Report data
    BugBounty -> Redis: Cache report
end
BugBounty --> UI: Report details
UI --> Researcher: Display status: "Pending Triage"

@enduml